Title: Tex Hangin' Out Button Down Shirt
Body (HTML):
<sections><section id="1"><sectionTitle>Details</sectionTitle><sectionBody>We refer to our flannel shirts as ‘Surf-flannels’ – not too heavy, not too dark, and not made to make you look like a lumberjack. Perfect to wear Hangin’ Out, unbuttoned with a tee, or buttoned-up and layered under a vest.
